      <title>美国与挪威签署协议从北极发射卫星</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/us-signs-deal-with-norway-to-launch-satellites-from-the-arctic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国和挪威签署一项协议，允许从北欧国家位于北极的安岛太空港发射美国卫星。]]></description>
